6:
Great job today, you guys!
Bottoms up!
15:
All right, all right...
Let's not get too rowdy now.
19:
I've gotta say, that trek through
the ruins was no joke!
22:
Considering all the treasure we found,
I'd say it was more than worth it!
And I couldn't have done it without
you guys!
25:
First round's on me, boys! Alk and I will
be having juice, of course.
28:
What's all this about, Yuna? You too
good to hang out with us anymore?
29:
Yeah, Yuna! How's about you treat us
to a round too, eh?
32: Who the hell are these guys?
36:
Oh, hmm... I'm not sure
if I have enough.
41:
Wait, don't actually give them
anything!
43:
So yer broke after all, huh?
Figured as much, seein' as yer always
hangin' out with grannies!
44:
Yeah. Sucks that you aren't puttin'
that pretty face of yours to better use
if you know what I mean!
59:
...It's fine, Nimbus. Don't let those two
spoil our celebration.
64: Sure you wanna let them off like that?
68:
Well, you know how people are when
they're hungry... right?
72: Hmph. Fine, if you say so.
74:
That's right, sit down. Better watch
what you say to a human next time,
furball.
87:
If you've got a problem with beastfolk,
you've got a problem with ME!
90:
Oh? Izzat so? Who the hell do you
think you are, talkin' to me like that?
100:
Whoa, that mug's completely
smashed. Ouch.
105:
You ought to be ashamed of yourself,
spitting that drivel here—We're ALL
adventurers here, human or not!
108:
You just made a huge mistake, you
little brat!
118:
Yeesh. You totally went demon-mode
on them, huh?
122:
Oops. Sorry, guys... I guess I kinda lost
myself there, huh?
127:
No, don't be sorry. You showed some
real heart there, kid.
132:
Y-you think so? I mean, if you say so,
then I guess I must've done
something right!
134:
Now then! We've made a fine mess
here, so... Let's get to cleaning,
shall we?
139: *sigh* Maybe a little too much heart.
